data.description: The picturesque view from the living room in this home is spectacular!  This large and modern home features four bedrooms all generously sized, plus an additional office!  Situated on two levels, upstairs is where most of the action is with a fantastic kitchen, dining area with door to private deck great waiting for your BBQ grill!  The master suite features a walk in closet, and bath with a tub and also a shower!  There is a full bathroom with laundry area upstairs, two more bedrooms and the office.  The living room is huge and offers space for the biggest of couches. Downstairs you will find a great storage room, fourth bedroom and a full bathroom.  There is a second living area, and of course two car garage.  The lot offers privacy and space, as well as room to park.  Schedule your showing today!
